race.comment: WHISKEY MISS (13) excellent return when shedding her maiden status with a dominant victory over 1210m at Lismore. Can go on with it this prep and gets every chance from the low draw. LIMAHULI (2) blinkers go on for the first time from the better gate after chipping away late with the 62kg when sixth over 1200m at Ipswich. Value chance. VETOED (12) recorded yet another minor placing last time out when third over 1310m at Lismore. Great chance to go a couple better. HIGH CLASS ROLLER (6) resumes and whilst not a noted first-up performer, gets a chance to feature here. In the mix from the good draw.
